I'm a pretty sorry excuse for a
great-great-grandpa.

1426
01:13:10,954 --> 01:13:14,398
Are you kidding? A minute ago,
I thought I was related to a murderer.

1427
01:13:14,423 --> 01:13:16,496
You're a total upgrade.

1428
01:13:16,838 --> 01:13:18,582
My whole life...

1429
01:13:18,607 --> 01:13:21,012
there's been something
that made me different.

1430
01:13:21,065 --> 01:13:23,435
And I never knew
