01:20:33,687 --> 01:20:34,775
Hurry, come on!

1541
01:20:37,144 --> 01:20:38,833
Ladies and gentleman!

1542
01:20:38,878 --> 01:20:44,865
The one. The only.
Ernesto de la Cruz!

